title: AI, Quantum, And The World Order
description: In 2026, the global tech race gets even more real. Lindsay Gorman — Managing Director of GMF’s Technology Program and former White House tech adviser — breaks down the US-China competition on AI and quantum, the future of TikTok, and why the new year could redefine global power. (Source: Bloomberg)
